: "chronicling america", "url": "https://www.loc.gov/collections/chronicling-america/?fo=json"}, {"count": 3225157, "title": "serial and government publications division", "url": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=partof:serial+and+government+publications+division&fo=json"}], "partof_collection": ["chronicling america"], "partof_division": ["serial and government publications division"], "partof_title": ["the montgomery advertiser (montgomery, ala.) 1885-1982"], "place_of_publication": "Montgomery, Ala.", "publication_frequency": ["daily"], "raw_lccn": "sn 84020645 ", "reel_numbers": ["00513684265"], "resources": [{"files": 12, "image": "https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:ndnp:au:batch_au_jacobs_ver01:data:sn84020645:00513684265:1908042101:0277/full/pct:6.25/0/default.jpg", "url": "https://www.loc.gov/resource/sn84020645/1908-04-21/ed-1/", "word_coordinates": "https://tile.loc.gov/text-services/word-coordinates-service"}], "rights": ["<p>The Library of Congress believes that the newspapers in Chronicling America are in the public domain or have no known copyright restrictions.  Newspapers published in the United States more than 95 years ago are in the public domain in their entirety. Any newspapers in Chronicling America that were published less than 95 years ago are also believed to be in the public domain, but may contain some copyrighted third party materials. Researchers using newspapers published less than 95 years ago should be alert for modern content (for example, registered and renewed for copyright and published with notice) that may be copyrighted.  Responsibility for making an independent legal assessment of an item and securing any necessary permissions ultimately rests with persons desiring to use the item.</p>\n<p>The NEH awardee responsible for producing each digital object is presented in the Chronicling America page display, below the page image  \u2013 e.g. Image produced by the Library of Congress. For more information on current NDNP awardees, see <a href=\"https://www.loc.gov/ndnp/listawardees.html\">https://www.loc.gov/ndnp/listawardees.html</a>.</p>\n<p>For more information on Library of Congress policies and disclaimers regarding rights and reproductions, see <a href=\"https://www.loc.gov/homepage/legal.html\">https://www.loc.gov/homepage/legal.html</a></p>"], "score": 14.141635, "shard": "05", "shelf_id": "sn84020645, 1908-04-21, Edition 1", "site": ["chroniclingamerica"], "source_group": "ndnp/au", "subject": ["montgomery county", "alabama", "montgomery (ala.)", "united states", "montgomery", "newspapers", "montgomery county (ala.)"], "subject_headings": ["Montgomery (Ala.)--Newspapers", "Montgomery County (Ala.)--Newspapers", "Alabama--Montgomery", "Alabama--Montgomery County", "United States--Alabama--Montgomery--Montgomery"], "subjects": [{"alabama": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:alabama&fo=json"}, {"montgomery": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:montgomery&fo=json"}, {"montgomery (ala.)": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:montgomery+%28ala.%29&fo=json"}, {"montgomery county": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:montgomery+county&fo=json"}, {"montgomery county (ala.)": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:montgomery+county+%28ala.%29&fo=json"}, {"newspapers": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:newspapers&fo=json"}, {"united states": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:united+states&fo=json"}], "timestamp": "2022-11-23T04:02:17.537Z", "title": "The Montgomery advertiser (Montgomery, Ala.), April 21, 1908", "type": ["issue"], "url": "https://www.loc.gov/item/sn84020645/1908-04-21/ed-1/"}, "locations": null, "method": "mets_filesec", "more_like_this": [{"access_restricted": false, "aka": ["http://www.loc.gov/item/sn83025485/1900-01-26/ed-1/", "http://www.loc.gov/resource/sn83025485/1900-01-26/ed-1/"], "batch": ["dlc_jean_ver01"], "campaigns": [], "contributor": ["library of congress, washington, dc"], "date": "1900-01-26", "dates": ["1900-01-26"], "description": ["Montgomery, Ala."], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2023-08-07T20:32:31.197Z", "group": ["ndnp/dlc-2020_now", "library-of-congress-washington-dc-awardee-8"], "hassegments": true, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/item/sn83025485/1900-01-26/ed-1/", "image_url": ["https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:ndnp:dlc:batch_dlc_jean_ver01:data:sn83025485:00220720457:1900012601:0001/full/pct:3.125/0/default.jpg#h=280&w=180", "https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:ndnp:dlc:batch_dlc_jean_ver01:data:sn83025485:00220720457:1900012601:0001/full/pct:6.25/0/default.jpg#h=560&w=361", "https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:ndnp:dlc:batch_dlc_jean_ver01:data:sn83025485:00220720457:1900012601:0001/full/pct:12.5/0/default.jpg#h=1120&w=722"], "index": 3, "language": ["english"], "location": ["united states", "alabama", "montgomery", "montgomery county"], "mime_type": ["image/jp2", "application/pdf", "text/xml", "image/jpeg"], "number": ["00220720457", "sn83025485", "1"], "numeric_shelf_id": 190001261, "online_format": ["image", "pdf", "online text"], "original_format": ["newspaper"], "other_title": ["Enterprise"], "partof": ["chronicling america", "the montgomery enterprise (montgomery, ala.) 1898-1???", "serial and government publications division"], "publication_frequency": ["weekly"], "score": 64.37011, "shelf_id": "sn83025485, 1900-01-26, Edition 1", "site": ["chroniclingamerica"], "subject": ["montgomery county", "african american newspapers", "alabama", "african americans", "african american", "montgomery (ala.)", "united states", "montgomery", "newspapers", "montgomery county (ala.)"], "timestamp": "2023-08-08T11:12:37.199Z", "title": "The Montgomery enterprise (Montgomery, Ala.), January 26, 1900", "type": ["issue"], "url": "https://www.loc.gov/item/sn83025485/1900-01-26/ed-1/"}, {"access_restricted": false, "aka": ["http://www.loc.gov/item/sn84020645/", "http://lccn.loc.gov/sn84020645", "https://search.catalog.loc.gov/instances/f8782173-611f-5377-892f-9465baf3c023"], "batch": ["au_julian_ver01"], "campaigns": [], "date": "1885", "description": ["Daily New ser. v. 21, no. 24 (Aug. 16, 1885)-new ser. v. 35, no. 323 (July 19, 1900) ; v. 71, no. 168 (July 20, 1900)-155th year, no. 47 (Nov. 21, 1982). On Saturday published as: Saturday morning, Apr. 2, 1977-Apr. 1, 1978; The Montgomery advertiser/Alabama journal, Apr. 8, 1978-Nov. 20, 1982. On Sunday published as: Montgomery advertiser and Alabama journal, Dec. 1, 1940-Nov. 21, 1982. Publisher varies: Advertiser Co., <1887> Numbering is irregular. Issues for Aug 16, 1885-July 19, 1899 called also Old ser. v. 54-v. 68. Also issued on microfilm from the University of Alabama Library, and the Library of Congress, Photoduplication Services. Archived issues are available in digital format from the Library of Congress Chronicling America online collection. Weekly eds.: Montgomery weekly advertiser, and: Weekly advertiser (Montgomery, Ala.), and: Montgomery advertiser (Montgomery, Ala. : Weekly). Advertiser (Montgomery, Ala.) 0745-3221 (DLC)sn 82008412 (OCoLC)9049482"], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2026-06-05T18:25:11.942Z", "group": ["newspaper-titles", "ndnp/newspapers", "catalog-split-14", "catalog", "united-states-newspaper-directory", "main-catalog-split-14"], "hassegments": false, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/item/sn84020645/", "image_url": [], "index": 4, "language": ["english"], "latlong": [32.376542, -86.2996608], "location": ["united states", "alabama", "montgomery", "montgomery county"], "location_str": "", "lonlat": [-86.2996608, 32.376542], "number": ["original", "2993-9143", "baylor univ", "panhandle-plains hist mus", "sn84023567", "2025-07-01t13:40:25.700000", "univ of texas at austin", "birmingham-jefferson libr", "2026-04-13t21:30:13", "sn86050480", "sn82008412", "http://www.loc.gov/item/sn84020645/1901-05-01/ed-1/", "univ of kentucky libr", "http://www.loc.gov/item/sn84020645/1927-12-31/ed-1/", "2685433", "kansas state hist soc, newsp proj", "sn86050479", "western rsv hist soc, newsp proj", "alabama newsp proj", "9739", "microfilm master", "online resource", "brigham young univ libr", "center for research libraries", "sn84020645", "center for res libr, newsp proj", "1", "2024-05-25t20:25:50.256555", "virginia historical society library", "library of congress", "duke univ libr", "microfilm service copy", "wisconsin hist soc, newsp proj", "sn84023549"], "original_format": ["newspaper"], "other_title": ["Saturday morning", "Montgomery advertiser and Alabama journal", "Montgomery advertiser/Alabama journal", "Daily advertiser"], "partof": ["chronicling america", "directory of u.s. newspapers in american libraries", "the montgomery advertiser (montgomery, ala.) 1885-1982", "serial and government publications division", "catalog"], "publication_frequency": ["daily"], "score": 61.58259, "shelf_id": "Newspaper AN", "site": ["chroniclingamerica", "usnd", "catalog"], "subject": ["montgomery county", "alabama", "montgomery (ala.)", "united states", "montgomery", "newspapers", "montgomery county (ala.)"], "timestamp": "2026-07-18T09:08:35.698Z", "title": "The Montgomery advertiser", "type": ["title"], "url": "https://www.loc.gov/item/sn84020645/"}, {"access_restricted": false, "aka": ["http://www.loc.gov/item/2013254326/"], "campaigns": [], "date": "1898", "dates": ["[1898 TO 1999]"], "description": ["Weekly Print began in 1898. Description based on: Volume 2, no. 20 (January 26, 1900); title from PDF masthead (Readex America's Historical Newspapers Web site, viewed May 22, 2013). Latest issue consulted: Volume 2, no. 20 (January 26, 1900) (viewed May 22, 2013)."], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2026-05-19T21:37:21.057Z", "group": ["ndnp/newspapers", "united-states-newspaper-directory"], "hassegments": false, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/item/2013254326/", "image_url": [], "index": 5, "language": ["english"], "location": ["united states", "alabama", "montgomery", "montgomery county"], "number": ["2026-04-13t21:30:13", "2835-6462", "online resource", "844394869", "2013254326"], "original_format": ["newspaper"], "other_title": ["Enterprise"], "partof": ["serial and government publications division", "the montgomery enterprise (montgomery, ala.) 1898-19?? [online resource]", "directory of u.s. newspapers in american libraries"], "publication_frequency": ["weekly"], "score": 52.468407, "shelf_id": "ISSN RECORD AN", "site": ["usnd"], "subject": ["montgomery county", "alabama", "african american newspapers", "african americans", "african american", "montgomery (ala.)", "united states", "montgomery", "newspapers", "montgomery county (ala.)"], "timestamp": "2026-05-26T20:48:57.173Z", "title": "The Montgomery enterprise", "type": ["title"], "url": "https://www.loc.gov/item/2013254326/"}, {"access_restricted": false, "aka": ["http://www.loc.gov/item/2023270666/"], "campaigns": [], "date": "1885", "dates": ["[1885 TO 1982]"], "description": ["Daily Print began with new ser. v. 21, no. 24 (Aug. 16, 1885); ceased November 21, 1982. On Saturday published as: Saturday morning, Apr. 2, 1977-Apr. 1, 1978; The Montgomery advertiser/Alabama journal, Apr. 8, 1978-Nov. 20, 1982. On Sunday published as: Montgomery advertiser and Alabama journal, Dec. 1, 1940-Nov. 21, 1982. Publisher varies: Screws, Cory & Glass, August 16, 1885-; The Advertiser Co., <1887-1909> Numbering is irregular. New series, vol. 35, no. 323 (July 19, 1900) followed by vol. 71, no. 168 (July 20, 1900). Issues for Aug 16, 1885-July 19, 1899 called also old series v. 54-v. 68. Also issued on microfilm from the University of Alabama Library, and the Library of Congress, Photoduplication Services. Weekly eds.: Montgomery weekly advertiser, and: Weekly advertiser (Montgomery, Ala.), and: Montgomery advertiser (Montgomery, Ala. : Weekly). Volume LXXII, Number 125 (June 1, 1901); title from mashead (Chroniclingamerica.loc.gov, viewed August 10, 2023). Volume LXXX, Number 365 (December 31, 1909) (Chroniclingameri